thread.title: BRIEF-Bahrain National Holding FY Profit Falls

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Bahrain National Holding FY Profit Falls

organizations.name: brief-bahrain national holding fy profit falls feb 27

text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - BAHRAIN NATIONAL HOLDING COMPANY :
* FY NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO SHAREHOLDERS 2.1 MILLION DINARS VERSUS 3.9 MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* BOARD PROPOSES FY CASH DIVIDEND OF 12 FILS PER SHARE * BOARD PROPOSES FY STOCK DIVIDEND OF 5 SHARES FOR EVERY 100 SHARES
* FY GROSS INSURANCE PREMIUMS 28.9 MILLION DINARS VERSUS 27.6 MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO Source: ( bit.ly/2GQHC6x ) Source: ( bit.ly/2FzlG0i ) Further company coverage: (Bengaluru Newsroom; +1 646 223 8780; )
